		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">玄文兽进行左右双爪交替攻击，依次造成<span color="#7fffd7">50%,60%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="739" y="511" width="407" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">玄文兽翻动身子，劈出一刀界风尖刃，造成<span color="#7fffd7">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="799" width="425" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">玄文兽进入追逐状态，若追逐至玩家处，则立即进行划击和翻击两段攻击，依次造成<span color="#7fffd7">60%,100%</span><span>伤害；若连续追逐25m以上，则停止追逐，施放扫尾造成</span><span color="#7fffd7">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/玄文兽.assets/Image_13.png')" x="719" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/玄文兽.assets/Image_14.png')" x="719" y="426">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/玄文兽.assets/Image_15.png')" x="719" y="714">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/玄文兽.assets/Image_16.png')" x="1391" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">玄文兽蓄力，用力使出右爪撕划，造成<span color="#7fffd7">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
