		<RichText x="1410" y="511" width="439" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">玄文兽唤出4枚浮仙之露，全部朝玩家处发射，均造成<span color="#7fbfff">25%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
